channel.title: Washing And Baking :: CID guide website
channel.description: These steps will use the two black machines next to the formlabs printer. Image with labels. First, take your pieces and place them in the washing basin. image Click the knob to power the machine on, and then click it again to start the washing. You can change the settings with the dial but they will be set up for washing for you. Image. Once your pieces are done washing, you can take them out and move them into the second black box, to bake them.
